  <brief_title>Surgical Prevention of Anastomotic Recurrence by Excluding Mesentery in Crohn's Disease</brief_title>
  <acronym>SuPREMeCD</acronym>
  <official_title>A New Anastomotic Technique After Ileocecal Resection for Crohn's Disease. Kono-s Anastomosis vs Stapled Side-to-side Anastomosis: a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
